I"k<h3 id="epilogue">Epilogue</h3>

<h2 id="a-better-way-is-possible">A better way is possible.</h2>

<p>It will take more effort. It won’t be as efficient. It may even cost you more money. However, it could lead to a healthier society of people who aren’t preyed upon by the designs they interact with.</p>

<p>We have a choice to pursue design either with hope or with fear.</p>

<p>May we always choose <em>hope</em>.</p>

<p>Hopeful design teaches us that there are real people in real places existing in real time behind <em>everything</em> we create.</p>

<p>May we design with purpose.</p>

<p><br /><br /></p>
